                    <h3>
                        <a style="text-decoration: none" href="" class="typewrite" data-period="2000" data-type='[ "Welcome to Kostify, worlds best cost estimation system.", "Simplify your logistics services with our top-notch buyer-seller interactivity", "Over 100 million downloads in first 10 days of launch"]'>
                            <span class="wrap"></span>
